OL,3,CFerry in auto-pilot for collision
OL,4,Cwhich killed three, prosecution say
OL,6,FWarnings were flashing on a Condor
OL,7,FFerry for up to 10 minutes before a
OL,8,Fcollision with a much smaller fishing
OL,9,Fboat that killed three people, the
OL,10,Fprosecution has told Jersey's Royal
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FIn his opening statement, Crown
OL,14,FAdvocate Matthew Maletroit says the
OL,15,Fferry - which is 184 times larger than
OL,16,Fthe L'Ecume II trawler - was left in
OL,17,Fautopilot and travelling at full speed
OL,18,Fat the time of the collision in
OL,19,FDecember 2022.
