OL,3,CFerry in auto-pilot for collision
OL,4,Cwhich killed three, prosecution say
OL,6,FHe argues that human error and the
OL,7,F"negligent actions" of the two Condor
OL,8,Fstaff on duty, Lewis Peter Carr from
OL,9,FSunderland and Artur Sevash-Zade, a
OL,10,FUkrainian national, caused the deaths
OL,11,Fof the three fishermen - Larry
OL,12,FSimyunn, Jervis Baligat and Michael
OL,13,FMichieli.
OL,15,FThe prosecutor says the "evidence
OL,16,Fshows a reckless disregard for safety".
OL,18,FMr Carr and Mr Sevash-Zade are on
OL,19,Ftrial, each charged with triple
OL,20,Fmanslaughter, and have both pleaded
OL,21,Fnot guilty to all counts.
