OL,3,CFerry in auto-pilot for collision
OL,4,Cwhich killed three, prosecution say
OL,6,FAdvocate Maletroit says the weather
OL,7,Fwas clear on the day of the incident,
OL,8,Fwith no wind and good visibility.
OL,10,FThe prosecutor adds there was "very
OL,11,Flittle traffic on the sea" when the
OL,12,Fcollision happened between the L'Ecume
OL,13,FII fishing vessel and the Commodore
OL,14,FGoodwill Condor Ferry, four nautical
OL,15,Fmiles off Jersey's St Ouen coastline.
