OL,3,CFerry in auto-pilot for collision
OL,4,Cwhich killed three, prosecution say
OL,6,FAt the time of impact, 5:35am on
OL,7,FThursday 8 December 2022, Advocate
OL,8,FMaletroit states that the ferry was
OL,9,Ftravelling at "double speed" of 18.5
OL,10,Fknots or 21.5 mph to make up for
OL,11,Frunning late.
OL,13,FHe says the "collision should never
OL,14,Fhave occurred" and the L'Ecume II boat
OL,15,Fwas left with "catastrophic damage",
OL,16,Fsinking instantly.
