OL,3,CFerry in auto-pilot for collision
OL,4,Cwhich killed three, prosecution say
OL,6,FAdvocate Maletroit says the "risk was
OL,7,Fobvious and there was ample time to
OL,8,Favoid it", stating they only realised
OL,9,Fand reacted seconds before impact,
OL,10,Fwhich was too late.
OL,12,FThe prosecutor explains that Mr Carr
OL,13,Finitiated a late turn, but steering
OL,14,Fonly switched from automatic to manual
OL,15,Fminutes after the collision when the
OL,16,FCaptain returned from a mandatory rest
OL,17,Fbreak and took over.
